  "release_notes": "Adds diagnostic logging for the Microsoft Store subscription gate so first-purchase failures surface a real reason in startup_log.txt instead of a silent generic error — needed to debug ARM64 Store purchase failures. Refreshes the welcome / paywall window with the Modern Blue theme and reframes it around the 7-day free trial: rounded card, themed buttons, friendlier copy. The subscription gate logic itself is unchanged; trial state is honored by the same is_active flag from Microsoft Store, so the 7-day trial works as soon as the Add-on is configured with one in Partner Center.",
